ygData.msgSnippet: Salutations Dr. Mom ! OK are you a doctor like an MD or a PhD. College was something I had trouble with as well. OK, I did get a bachlors but I changed majors
ygData.messageBody:
Salutations "Dr. Mom"!

OK are you a doctor like an MD or a PhD. College was
something I had trouble with as well. OK, I did get a
bachlors but I changed majors four or five times and
it took forever. Then I worked on my masters but I
kind of bounced back and fourth on that and never
finished it. I did end up with enough credit for a PhD
though plus some if I had ever stayed on one thing
long enough.

On the up side I have a very interesting education and
I have studied such things as Cinema, Biomedical
Engineering, Medieval Literature, Theology, and
Chemistry.

I'm way higher than anyone I know in RL who plays.
Maybe I'm the only real addict. A couple are gaining
on me though.

I like you already. Too bad you aren't on the Xegony
server. I would send you tells and bug you.

/Hugs
Bran
